Package: FastSegmentation
Title: Unsupervised Cell Segmentation by Fast Gaussian Processes 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Blythe", "King", , "blyking@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Haoran", "Yan", , "hyan82@gatech.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Mengyang", "Gu", , "mengyang@pstat.ucsb.edu", role = c("aut))
Description: Functions for performing fast Gaussian process-based segmentation of microscopy images using spatial smoothing and data-driven thresholding. Code based on the methods described in Baracaldo, L., King, B., Yan, H., Lin, Y., Miolane, N., & Gu, M. (2025). Unsupervised cell segmentation by fast Gaussian Processes. arXiv preprint arXiv:2505.18902.
